# Shared mailmap applied to every mirror during git log (--use-mailmap).
#
# Populate this file once with `ingest seed-mailmap`, which dumps every
# distinct "Name <email>" seen across all mirrors here. A human then dedupes
# identities by rewriting lines in canonical form, e.g.:
#
#   Canonical Name <canonical@example.com> <old-alias@example.com>
#   Canonical Name <canonical@example.com> Old Name <old@example.com>
#
# Blank / comment lines are ignored by git.
